nhc_headline: ...CATEGORY 4 HUMBERTO WILL PRODUCE DANGEROUS SURF FOR BERMUDA AND MOST OF THE U.S. EAST COAST THIS WEEK...
summary: ...CATEGORY 4 HUMBERTO WILL PRODUCE DANGEROUS SURF FOR BERMUDA AND MOST OF THE U.S. EAST COAST THIS WEEK... As of 2:00 AM AST Mon Sep 29 the center of Humberto was located near 26.7, -66.6 with movement NW at 14 mph. The minimum central pressure was 928 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 140 mph.
